{"tid":1853883,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［小家到死］大新銀行暫時更改全線45間分行營業時間","createTime":"2020-01-31T08:17:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T14:35:59.000Z","uid":1082,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e4969b90a2e70db3d410aff131d7068572e7700a","tid":1853883,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T08:17:15.000Z","msg":"大新銀行宣布，為更好保障客戶及員工的健康利益，明日起至下星期六，即2月1日至8日，暫時更改全線45間分行營業時間。<br />\n<br />\n平日分行營業時間縮短，由早上10時至下午3時。周六分行營業時間由早上10時至下午1時。<br />\n<br />\n大新強調，非常重視客戶及員工安全，會密切監察所有員工健康狀況。而為盡量減低感染風險，銀行建議客戶使用電話理財服務、網上及流動理財服務，處理帳戶事宜。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">會唔會小家左啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"1ef23881b03b1a83b1b56bca037448d5fa1aab5d","tid":1853883,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T08:19:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁撚小家，直接改名做小家銀行啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"034b1974cdeb324642ba55d44210007ebbbe4c77","tid":1853883,"uid":146344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T08:20:22.000Z","msg":"所有員工今明星期都要番工 不論front or back"},{"pid":"33c0b0a6c713412cf18d8cd1295a0ec5a8df9dcd","tid":1853883,"uid":148704,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T08:23:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">大新強調，非常重視客戶及員工安全</span>，會密切監察所有員工健康狀況。而為盡量減低感染風險，銀行建議客戶使用電話理財服務、網上及流動理財服務，處理帳戶事宜。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大新連home office都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e0ca62f95a22340035bb38e3fa5a36b189f1b50","tid":1853883,"uid":1082,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"33c0b0a6c713412cf18d8cd1295a0ec5a8df9dcd","tid":1853883,"uid":148704,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"re